  <rdf:type rdf:resource="#Evidence"/>
  <evidenceContent rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">6 How do we secure personal information? We take significant and appropriate security measures including physical technological and procedural measures to help to safeguard your personal information and to prevent unauthorized access and disclosure In addition we use industry-standard technology such as Secure Sockets Layer SSL encryption technology in the transmission of certain sensitive personal information designed to prevent unauthorized persons from gaining access to your personal information and as technology develops we intend to take additional measures to improve security</evidenceContent>
